Blurred lines.

If you known me for awhile, you know I’ve been on this skin journey for a awhile… suffering from bad acne, dark scaring, & hyper pigmentation. Outside of doing consistent facials and a proper skin care routine, I saw the most dramatic change after doing a chemical peel. This one I did at @profile.aw from @theperfectdermapeel and as you can see from day 1 to day 6 there is some dramatic exfoliation of my first layer of skin, which got rid of a lot of dark pigmentation,that I didn’t think would go away…as well as better skin tone & texture. It was definitely a leap of faith, because with dark skin tone, you have to be very careful. My skin has been the best it’s been since popping out the womb 🤰🏽
